HOTRON PRECISION said unconsolidated sales
in June rose 29.58% to NT$81,877,000 from NT$63,185,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales             81,877           63,185    
YOY%              29.58%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            580,114          388,746    
YOY%              49.23% 
=================================================================
 